# Keep the build context small and hermetic: the Dockerfile installs deps from the lockfile
# and generates the contract artifacts itself, so none of the following must leak in.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage
packages/contract/src/generated

.git
.github
.idea
.vscode

# Secrets / local env — never bake into an image layer.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Test-only assets and docs are not needed to build the runtime image.
**/*.log
